🚨 What is Error Handling? 

Error handling is the process of detecting, managing, and responding to errors in a program so that the application doesn’t crash and behaves safely.

Interviewr Definition :
“Error handling ensures that the application can gracefully recover from unexpected situations instead of crashing, improving reliability and user experience.”

